<lb n="0452a12" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0452a13" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 180</head>
<lb n="0452a14" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0452002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0452002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452002"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>過去<note n="0452003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔世〕－【三】</note><note n="0452003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452003"><lem>世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>佛分衛經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0452a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0452a16" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0452004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔西晉…三藏〕七字－【宋】</note><app word-count="7" n="0452004"><lem>西晉<note n="0452005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔月氏國〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0452005"><lem>月氏國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0452006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三藏＋（法師）【元】【明】</note><app n="0452006"><lem>三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">三藏法師</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0452a17" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT03p0452a1701">佛言。<note n="0452007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">過＋（去）【三】</note><note n="0452007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＋（去）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452007"><lem>過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">過去</rdg></app>世有佛入城分衛。與尊弟子諸菩
<lb n="0452a18" ed="T"/>薩俱。弟子菩薩姿容相好皆悉端正。如本所
<lb n="0452a19" ed="T"/>行各得其道。有一母人&CB00775;<note n="0452008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">身＝娠【元】【明】</note><app n="0452008"><lem>身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">娠</rdg></app>數月。見佛及
<lb n="0452a20" ed="T"/>僧有所至<note n="0452009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">奏＝湊【三】</note><note n="0452009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奏＝湊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452009"><lem>奏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">湊</rdg></app>。心自計願我所懷子生。如此
<lb n="0452a21" ed="T"/>使為沙門佛弟子。日月滿足即生安隱。兒亦
<lb n="0452a22" ed="T"/>姝好與眾人異。母以恩愛無<note n="0452010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">意＝厭【三】</note><note n="0452010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝厭【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452010"><lem>意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">厭</rdg></app>令兒行作沙
<lb n="0452a23" ed="T"/>門。中有覺意。即自念言。我前有願。若我生
<lb n="0452a24" ed="T"/>子當使為道。兒今已生有異凡人。令我安隱
<lb n="0452a25" ed="T"/>復無惡露。不可戀<note n="0452011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嫪＝&CB00387;【三】</note><note n="0452011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嫪＝&CB00387;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452011"><lem>嫪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00387;</rdg></app>恩愛之故違我本心。
<lb n="0452a26" ed="T"/>子年七歲家復貧狹。即作二人飯具及三法
<lb n="0452a27" ed="T"/>衣。手持澡瓶自將其子行詣佛所。稽首佛足
<lb n="0452a28" ed="T"/>前白佛言。願哀我子使為沙門。令後得道身
<lb n="0452a29" ed="T"/>形如佛。佛即聽之令作沙門。母以澡<note n="0452012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">灌＝罐【三】</note><note n="0452012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">灌＝罐【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452012"><lem>灌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">罐</rdg></app>前
<pb n="0452b" id="T03.0180.0452b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0452b01" ed="T"/><note n="0452013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">洗＝酒【宋】</note><app n="0452013"><lem>洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">酒</rdg></app>兒手。應時九龍從瓶口出。吐水灌兒手
<lb n="0452b02" ed="T"/>中。澡訖殘水散兒頭上。水之潺<note n="0452014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">渧＝滴【三】</note><note n="0452014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渧＝滴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452014"><lem>渧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">滴</rdg></app>於兒頭
<lb n="0452b03" ed="T"/>上化成華蓋珠交絡帳。中有師子座上有坐
<lb n="0452b04" ed="T"/>佛。佛笑口中五色光出。照十億佛剎。還遶佛
<lb n="0452b05" ed="T"/>身從兒頂入。母以飯具前上佛并食其<note n="0452015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（子）【三】</note><note n="0452015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（子）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452015"><lem>子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">子子</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0452b06" ed="T"/>便發無上平等道意。應時十億佛剎為六<note n="0452016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">反＝返【三】</note><note n="0452016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452016"><lem>反</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">返</rdg></app>
<lb n="0452b07" ed="T"/>震動。眾剎諸佛皆自然現。佛以母飯飽。爾
<lb n="0452b08" ed="T"/>所佛及諸比丘僧皆等飽足。其飯如故亦不
<lb n="0452b09" ed="T"/>損減。母即歡喜。及無數天人皆得阿惟越致。
<lb n="0452b10" ed="T"/>時兒髮墮成為沙門。即亦得立不退轉地。母
<lb n="0452b11" ed="T"/>前白佛。今我所見有三可怪。我澡兒手九龍
<lb n="0452b12" ed="T"/>吐水。此一可怪。澡已殘水散兒頭上化成寶
<lb n="0452b13" ed="T"/>帳。及師子座上有坐佛。是二可怪。佛笑口
<lb n="0452b14" ed="T"/>中光從兒頂入。是三可怪。願佛為我分別說
<lb n="0452b15" ed="T"/>之。佛言。此兒<note n="0452017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00230;＝起【宋】，印【元】</note><note n="0452017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00230;＝起【宋】，＝印【元】</note><app n="0452017"><lem>&CB00230;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">起</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">印</rdg></app>後十四劫當得作佛。九龍
<lb n="0452b16" ed="T"/>當浴師子座華蓋寶帳。佛笑光從兒頂入。皆
<lb n="0452b17" ed="T"/>是其應。母聞佛言倍懷踊躍。後<note n="0452018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當＋（得）【三】</note><note n="0452018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＋（得）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452018"><lem>當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當得</rdg></app>作母人
<lb n="0452b18" ed="T"/>轉輪聖王。積七百世竟。其劫壽盡轉母人身。
<lb n="0452b19" ed="T"/>當得阿惟越致。佛言。是時小兒我身是。我
<lb n="0452b20" ed="T"/>今於世功德如是。諸天龍神一切人民聞佛
<lb n="0452b21" ed="T"/>所說。皆得阿惟越致。</p>
<lb n="0452b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT03p0452b2201">　無熱佛　性空佛　天王佛　金仁佛</p>
<lb n="0452b23" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0452019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0452019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452019"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>過去<note n="0452020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔世〕－【三】</note><note n="0452020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452020"><lem>世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>佛分衛經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>